    {
      "id": "710457",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "Bossrt",
        "uid": "101395"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t中国什么时候富了，人均GDP连欧盟一半都没有，同样黄种人的日本人均GDP都碾压中国，甚至被西方制裁的俄爹人均GDP都领先中国<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9paWxpLmlvL0pJdXhHa3UuanBn\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://iili.io/JIuxGku.jpg\">https://iili.io/JIuxGku.jpg</a> </div>",
      "date": "2023-12-05",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 1,
      "discussions": [
